snippet.title: XDefiant Launch Finally Confirmed! | (Open Beta Next Week!)
snippet.description:
The launch window for XDefiant was finally confirmed as well as the dates for the Open Beta (June 21-23) and a bunch of the launch and post launch content we can expect to see with the game! What are your current thoughts on XDefiant? 

Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/thexclusiveace

Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheXclusiveAce
